{"tid":1651912,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"正能量，戰區選","createTime":"2019-10-13T13:27:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T16:51:19.000Z","uid":3825,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f34709972c571ad93ec5d73cfe86539092504093","tid":1651912,"uid":3825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:27:38.000Z","msg":"我屌你啦，你覺得選舉主任會唔DQ你？你真係覺得呢個制度會公平咩？<br />\n<br />\n我認我太樂觀，五大訴求中嘅普選會令大家反思下咩叫高度自治...果時蘋果講血債票償比人屌以為大家會覺醒。結果呢大家都係關心個區選有冇得選.....<br />\n<br />\n<strong>光復香港，時代革命</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只係一個口號？<br />\n大家升級唔指係行動，思想上都可以一齊升級下嗎？<br />\n<br />\n明明政府就大台佢做咩你先會有咩嘅行動亦提醒緊大家，要做嘢...<br />\n<br />\n結果大家仲係關心死幾多人點點點，我明死左幾多人個個都想知（包括我）但可唔可以唔好當佢係主線...由六月開始已經背負緊人命嫁啦fced，大家都知而且起碼只少有二百萬人知啦⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n大家其實仲有好多嘢做....只少可以睇下咩叫和理非先<br />\n<br />\n利申：我係引戰狗，失敗撚，雨傘怨婦，分化撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBetween <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">願榮光歸香港</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d67e493add0b4e60e08fa4bdd8546a93c7d005","tid":1651912,"uid":3825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:46:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自推1/10"},{"pid":"fbfe1d107c72224a00da88955ddd9bfee9423afd","tid":1651912,"uid":3825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:46:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自推2/10"},{"pid":"f5ae2fcf779a0b4601790d2261c94d14a503b136","tid":1651912,"uid":3825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:46:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自推3/10"},{"pid":"e9e4dcd81bf80b3808a7f47af5e021b44f7a0230","tid":1651912,"uid":3825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:47:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\